com.cisco.mscviewer.model

Class Event

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cisco.mscviewer.model.Event

  • public class Event
extends java.lang.Object
    An Event represents an occurence of relevance for an Entity within a data model (see MSCDataModel. An Event is characterized by a timestamp, a label, a type.

        dm - the MSCDataModel this Event belongs to
        timestamp - the timestamp the event occurred at
        en - the Entity the event belong to
        label - the label associated to the event
        lineIndex - the index of the source line this event was generated from
        renderer - the EventRenderer associated to the event
        props - properties for the renderer
